import pytest
import random
from solution import *


def test_examples():
    assert add_const_130(0) == 130
    assert add_const_130(5) == 135
    assert add_const_130(-3) == 127


def test_randomized():
    random.seed(1001)
    for _ in range(50):
        n = random.randint(-300, 300)
        assert add_const_130(n) == n + 130
